{"id":142494,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/李敖之子因网瘾被北大会商/","date":"2011-04-02T06:00:28Z","modified":"2011-04-02T16:50:16Z","title":"李敖之子因网瘾被北大会商","content":"<p>《广州日报》报导，承认翻墙访问Facebook的李敖之子、北大经济学院学生李戡上了北大的“会商名单”。北大此前曾宣布从五月起对学业困难、思想偏激、心理脆弱、经济贫困、学籍异动、生活独立、网络成瘾、就业困难、罹患重大疾病、受到违纪处分等十类学生进行会商，李戡上榜的原因是“上网成性”。<img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/13d6929f/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%9D%8E%E6%95%96%E4%B9%8B%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%A0%E7%BD%91%E7%98%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E5%95%86&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F02%2F0132258%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%9D%8E%E6%95%96%E4%B9%8B%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%A0%E7%BD%91%E7%98%BE%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E5%95%86&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F02%2F0132258%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98747455034/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/13d6929f/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/98747455034/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/13d6929f/a2.img\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=WZe2dMamKFY:0VZOrQSpPqA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=WZe2dMamKFY:0VZOrQSpPqA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<p><strong>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):ziyouwangluo2011ATgmail.com